text: Karma Tshomo (born 10 October 1973), is an archer who internationally represented Bhutan Tshomo competed for Bhutan at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona, she finished 58th in the individual event, the highest out of the Bhutanese women's and the team finished 17th.Sports Reference Profile ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic archers of Bhutan Category:Archers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Bhutanese female archers
